{
  "stem": "1873.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 23.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Interesting that whenever I sleep in Santa Barbara, I'd wake up in the morning and look outside, seeing the ocean, an opposite thought would come.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe this is a dream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although I know, 99.9%, it's not a dream, but still.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was working there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always did look for a job I shouldn't be visible to the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it won't take too long to talk, but my last job, my longest job in Sobibor, was burning documents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They called me fireman in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a building.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a big incinerator inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the people, which were sorting, emptied the pockets from the pants and jackets, from the documents, they brought the papers to me in blankets, and I burned them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes they sneak in a blanket of money because didn't want to give it to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was burn it the first round.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, usually they threw the trash, the papers, in a special place, and I burned them at comes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when a guy would come with a blanket of money, I put it immediately in the fire.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Sobibor, money had no-- had no-- they used to-- I used to-- I-- we-- I used some money for some purpose.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I will, I will tell you because it's an interesting insight in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When a Dutch transport, or German, or a French transport, they didn't know they're going to die.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a Polish transport, they were aware.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as I said, still hope is with us to the last minute.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's a Polish book, which meant--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dies last.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is a true book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So people, knowing they were going-- nude, undressed, going to death, they still had, in there hand, some money.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
